Vendored content was split from the upstream single-file SKILL.md
into the following files under `references/`:

    a_stock_data_common.md      (intro + prerequisites + helpers + valuation
                                 formulas + research workflows + data-source
                                 priority + FAQ)
    a_stock_market_data.md      (Layer 1: mootdx + Tencent + Baidu K-line)
    a_stock_research.md         (Layer 2: Eastmoney + THS + iwencai)
    a_stock_signals.md          (Layer 3: THS hot stocks, Northbound, Baidu
                                 concept blocks, Eastmoney fund flow minute,
                                 dragon-tiger list, lockup calendar, industry
                                 ranking)
    a_stock_capital_flow.md     (Layer 4: margin trading, block trades,
                                 holder count, dividends, 120-day fund flow)
    a_stock_news.md             (Layer 5: Eastmoney stock news, CLS flash,
                                 Eastmoney global news)
    a_stock_fundamentals.md     (Layer 6: mootdx finance/F10, Eastmoney
                                 basic info, Sina financial statements)
    a_stock_filings.md          (Layer 7: cninfo full-text filings)

Modifications: each file has a frontmatter block added (upstream commit
SHA, version, date, license tag) and a "在 mx-skills 中的使用方式" header
note describing how the router invokes the inline-Python code blocks.
The original code and prose are otherwise unchanged.

